an%20Union%20as%20a%20member.%20Fifty-five%20countries%20from%20Africa%20are%20members%20of%20the%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20which%20currently%20holds%20the%20rotating%20presidency%20of%20the%20G20%2C%20had%20proposed%20including%20the%20African%20Union%20as%20a%20full%20member.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20plan%20for%20the%20future%20of%20the%20planet%20can%20be%20successful%20without%20the%20representation%20and%20recognition%20of%20all%20voices%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20said%20on%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfrica%20is%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20us%20even%20within%20the%20G20.%20One%20of%20the%20first%20things%20we%20did%20during%20our%20G20%20Presidency%20was%20to%20hold%20the%20%E2%80%98Voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%E2%80%99%20summit%2C%20which%20had%20enthusiastic%20participation%20from%20Africa%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20need%20to%20come%20out%20of%20a%20purely%20utilitarian%20worldview%20and%20embrace%20a%20Sarva%20Jana%20Hitaaya%2C%20Sarva%20Jana%20Sukhaaya%20(for%20the%20welfare%20of%20all%2C%20for%20the%20happiness%20of%20all)%20model.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20African%20Union%2C%20however%2C%20there%20is%20no%20consensus%20on%20whether%20joining%20the%20G20%20would%20be%20beneficial%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fsep%2F04%2Fafrican-union-likely-tobecome-21st-member-of-g20-2611449.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20%E2%80%9CAfrica%20is%20a%20large%20continent%20and%20the%20challenges%2C%20economy%20and%20communities%20are%20very%20diverse.%20In%20that%20context%2C%20we%20feel%20that%20this%20inclusion%20in%20the%20G20%20would%20not%20translate%20into%20anything%20for%20us%20in%20the%20literal%20sense.%20The%20Voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20must%20be%20heard%20but%20the%20inclusion%20in%20G20%20would%20not%20help%20in%20addressing%20the%20concerns.