eponderantly%20Punjabi%20army%20in%20the%20Punjab-dominated%20state%3B%20difficulties%20in%20framing%20the%20first%20constitution%20because%20of%20West%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20reluctance%20to%20concede%20the%20democratic%20rights%20of%20the%20numerically%20superior%20eastern%20wing%3B%20and%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20alliance%20with%20the%20Western%20bloc%20with%20a%20leading%20role%20for%20the%20army%20and%20large%20flows%20of%20US%20assistance%20to%20it%20in%20cash%20and%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20army%20has%20ruled%20the%20state%20directly%20for%2033%20years%20and%20exercised%20influence%20from%20behind%20the%20scenes%20during%20the%20remaining%20period.%20It%20has%20shown%20resilience%20in%20recovering%20from%20periodic%20setbacks%2C%20including%20its%20crushing%20defeat%20in%201971%2C%20using%20strong-arm%20tactics%20and%20intimidation%20to%20enforce%20its%20will.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20came%20as%20a%20surprise%20when%20its%20prot%C3%A9g%C3%A9%2C%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20revolted%20on%20being%20driven%20out%20of%20power%20in%202022%20after%20falling%20out%20with%20the%20former%20army%20chief%20Qamar%20Javed%20Bajwa%2C%20posing%20a%20challenge%20to%20Bajwa%20and%20his%20successor%2C%20Asim%20Munir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20time%2C%20it%20seemed%20that%20the%20army%20had%20finally%20come%20upon%20its%20comeuppance.%20The%20challenge%2C%20initially%20open%20criticism%20of%20the%20army%20leadership%2C%20took%20a%20violent%20turn%20after%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20on%20May%209%2C%202023.%20For%20two%20days%2C%20until%20his%20release%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20his%20supporters%20perpetrated%20violence%20of%20an%20unprecedented%20sweep%20and%20intensity%20against%20important%20military%20installations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fimran-khans-arrest-will-exacerbate-pakistans-multi-system-meltdown%5C%22%3EImran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Arrest%20Will%20Exacerbate%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Multi-System%20Meltdown%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImran%20Khan%20had%20clearly%20overplayed%20his%20hand.%20Asim%20Munir%20used%20the%20violence%20to%20consolidate%20his%20position.%20He%20obtained%20the%20support%20of%20his%20senior%20commanders%20and%20the%20civilian%20set-up%20to%20take%20strict%20action%20against%20the%20perpetrators%20and%20instigators%20of%20the%20violence%2C%20including%20through%20trials%20in%20military%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20took%20action%20against%20a%20number%20of%20senior%20army%20officers%20sympathetic%20to%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20including%20the%20dismissal%20of%20a%20Lieutenant%20General.%20Many%20senior%20PTI%20leaders%20were%20coerced%20into%20abandoning%20Imran%20Khan.%20Consequently%2C%20when%20he%20was%20arrested%20again%20in%20early%20August%20after%20his%20conviction%20in%20one%20of%20the%20many%20cases%20pending%20against%20him%2C%20there%20was%20not%20a%20whimper%20of%20protest%20from%20his%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGranted%20bail%20by%20the%20Islamabad%20High%20Court%2C%20he%20has%20been%20detained%20in%20yet%20another%20case.%20The%20army%20is%20bent%20on%20removing%20him%20from%20the%20political%20equation%2C%20at%20least%20for%20the%20next%20election.%20Its%20task%20may%20be%20rendered%20easier%20when%20the%20current%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20who%20is%20seen%20as%20pro-Imran%2C%20retires%20in%20mid-September%20to%20make%20way%20for%20Qazi%20Faez%20Isa%2C%20who%20is%20ill-disposed%20towards%20Imran%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20the%20government%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Democratic%20Movement%20(PDM)%20that%20was%20formed%20in%202020%2C%20inter%20alia%2C%20to%20resist%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20interference%20in%20political%20and%20civilian%20affairs%20has%20ended%20up%20strengthening%20its%20hand%20through%20amendments%20to%20the%20Official%20Secrets%20Act%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20Army%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmendments%20to%20the%20former%20make%20unauthorised%20disclosure%20of%20identities%20of%20members%20of%20intelligence%20agencies%20a%20punishable%20offence%2C%20give%20a%20role%20to%20officials%20of%20the%20intelligence%20agencies%20in%20investigating%20cases%20of%20its%20violation%20and%20in%20the%20process%20entering%20and%20searching%20a%20place%C2%A0or%20person%20without%20a%20warrant%20and%20seizing%20any%20document%20or%20electronic%20device%20by%20way%C2%A0of%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmendments%20to%20the%20latter%20make%20defamation%20of%20the%20army%20a%C2%A0punishable%20offence%2C%20bar%20ex-servicemen%20from%20engaging%20in%20activities%20in%20conflict%C2%A0with%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20interest%20(a%20number%20of%20ex-servicemen%20were%20among%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%C2%A0supporters)%20and%20make%20provisions%20of%20the%20Act%20applicable%20notwithstanding%20anything%20inconsistent%20in%20any%20other%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20army%20which%20already%20has%C2%A0a%20veritable%20business%20empire%2C%20has%20been%20authorised%20to%20carry%20out%20activities%20related%C2%A0to%20national%20development%20and%20generate%20proceeds%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20its%20serving%20and%C2%A0retired%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20past%20economic%20actions%20%E2%80%93%20some%20of%20which%20were%20questioned%20by%20courts%20from%20time%20to%20time-%20have%20been%20legalised.%20Weeks%20before%20the%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20government%20laid%20down%20office%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20Army%20Chief%20announced%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20Special%20Investment%20Facilitation%20Council%20(SIFC)%20that%2C%20it%20was%20claimed%2C%20would%20attract%20billions%20of%20dollars%20of%20investment%20from%20the%20Gulf%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20premature%20to%20describe%20the%20SIFC%20as%20a%20game-changer.%C2%A0Similar%20past%20initiatives%20have%20come%20a%20cropper.%20Asim%20Munir%20has%20been%C2%A0emphasising%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20economy%20in%20his%20speeches.%20The%20army%20has%C2%A0also%20got%2045%2C000%20acres%20of%20land%20from%20the%20Punjab%20government%20for%20%E2%80%98corporate%C2%A0agriculture%20farming%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20clarity%20on%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20next%20election%2C%20due%20constitutionally%20by%20the%20first%20week%20of%20November.%20The%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20government%20hurriedly%20approved%20the%20results%20of%20the%202022%20census%20at%20the%20fag%20end%20of%20its%20tenure%2C%20thereby%20necessitating%20a%20fresh%20delimitation%20of%20constituencies%2C%20a%20time-consuming%20exercise%2C%20which%20would%20push%20the%20polls%20to%20at%20least%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20army%20has%20got%20installed%20a%20constitutionally%20mandated%20caretaker%20government%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20election%20under%20the%20Prime%20Ministership%20of%20Anwaar-ul-Haq%20Kakar%2C%20a%20Baloch%20politician%20known%20to%20be%20close%20to%20it.%20A%20law%20enacted%20by%20the%20outgoing%20government%20confers%20extra%20powers%20on%20the%20caretaker%20set%20up%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20equipping%20it%20to%20stabilise%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20the%20apprehension%20of%20a%20prolonged%20tenure%20for%20the%20army-backed%20caretaker%20government.%20For%20now%2C%20the%20army%20is%20in%20firm%20control.%20Asim%20Munir%20would%20like%20to%20see%20a%20hung%20National%20Assembly%20after%20the%20next%20election%2C%20in%20which%20he%20could%20craft%20a%20majority%20of%20his%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20election%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20heavily%20managed%20affair%2C%20thus%20resulting%20in%20a%20government%20bereft%20of%20political%20legitimacy%20and%20incapable%20of%20dealing%20effectively%20with%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20myriad%20problems%2C%20notably%20the%20wobbly%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-army-imran-khan-scorned%5C%22%3EHell%20Hath%20No%20Fury%20Like%20the%20Pakistan%20Army%20Scorned%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20challenge%20to%20the%20army%20was%20not%20a%20democratic%20revolution.%20He%20was%20himself%20a%20creation%20of%20the%20army.%20More%20importantly%2C%20Pakistan%20has%20so%20far%20produced%20no%20civilian%20leader%20capable%20of%20spearheading%20a%20mass%20uprising%20against%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20relatively%20small%20groups%20of%20PTI%20protestors%20attacked%20several%20army%20installations%20in%20May%2C%20there%20was%20no%20mass%20upsurge.%20The%20redressal%20of%20the%20long-standing%20civil-military%20imbalance%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20as%20and%20when%20it%20comes%20about%2C%20would%20be%20the%20culmination%20of%20a%20process%20and%20not%20an%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20little%20leverage%20over%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20internal%20developments%20and%20has%20dealt%20with%20all%20governments%20there%2C%20including%20military%20dictators%2C%20to%20manage%20the%20difficult%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20all%20that%20we%20can%20do%20is%20to%20keep%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20the%20events%20in%20Pakistan%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20growing%20instability%20there%20does%20not%20impact%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20further%20stabilisation%20of%20the%20bilateral%20relationship%20beyond%20the%20restored%20ceasefire%20of%20February%202021%20must%20await%20greater%20clarity%20on%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20internal%20dynamics.%20Though%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20control%20has%20been%20reinforced%20by%20the%20recent%20developments%2C%20Asim%20Munir%20may%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20change%20the%20policy%20of%20tactical%20restraint%20vis%20a%20vis%20India%20adopted%20by%20his%20predecessor%20because%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20complex%20internal%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESharat%20Sabharwal%20is%20a%20former%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20author%20of%20the%20book%3C%2Fem%3E%20India%E2%80%99s%20Pakistan%20Conundrum%3A%20Managing%20a%20Complex%20Relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fworld%2Farmys-control-reinforced-in-pakistan-2671057%5C%22%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20with%20permission.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693816198000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04135237%2Fgallery-image2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistani-military-national-politics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20army%2C%20which%20already%20has%20a%20veritable%20business%20empire%2C%20has%20been%20authorised%20to%20carry%20out%20activities%20related%20to%20national%20development.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistani-military-national-politics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Not%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20but%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang%20to%20Attend%20G20%20Summit%20in%20India%2C%20China%20Confirms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F04%2FLi_Keqiang-19052015_-_2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Beijing%20has%20said%20today%20that%20Chinese%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang%20will%20attend%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20officially%20confirming%20speculation%20that%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20will%20be%20giving%20the%20meet%20a%20miss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20invitation%20of%20India%2C%20Chinese%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang%20will%20attend%20the%20G20%20Summit%20from%20September%209%20to%2010%20in