with%20the%20traffic%20police%20to%20ensure%20smooth%20flow%20of%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fg20-summit-new-delhi-travelling-during-g20-heres-how-you-can-reach-railway-stations-airport-4357021%5C%22%3ETravelling%20During%20G20%3F%20Here's%20How%20You%20Can%20Reach%20Railway%20Stations%2C%20Airport%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20curbs%20and%20regulations%20will%20cover%20the%20New%20Delhi%20district%2C%20and%20come%20into%20effect%20from%20the%20night%20of%20September%207%2C%20days%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgurugram-traffic-police-advisory-traffic-movement-restricted-on-national-highway-48-in-gurugram-for-g20-summit-delhi-g20-summit-delhi-g20-gurugram-g20-4355164%5C%22%3EG20%20summit%3C%2Fa%3E%20begins.%20But%20traffic%20flow%20will%20be%20affected%20in%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20national%20capital.%20Railways%20have%20also%20announced%20cancellation%20of%20several%20trains%20in%20the%20Northern%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20planning%20to%20go%20to%20Connaught%20Place%2C%20or%20other%20areas%20in%20central%20Delhi%2C%20it's%20better%20to%20plan%20in%20advance%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fg20-summit-these-delhi-metro-stations-to-remain-closed-from-september-8-10-4356900%5C%22%3Euse%20the%20Metro%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Here%20are%20answers%20to%20some%20critical%20questions%20that%20will%20help%20you%20navigate%20the%20curbs%20smoothly%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20markets%20will%20remain%20closed%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20summit%20will%20be%20organised%20at%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20in%20Pragati%20Maidan%20on%20September%209%20and%2010.%20So%2C%20all%20establishments%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20area%20will%20remain%20close%20for%20these%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20declared%20Dhaula%20Kuan%2C%20Khan%20Market%2C%20Janpath%20and%20Bhikaji%20Cama%20Place%20as%20%26quot%3Bsensitive%20areas%26quot%3B.%20However%2C%20clarifying%20the%20move%2C%20Surender%20Yadav%2C%20Special%20CP%20(Traffic)%2C%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2Flive%2F%3Fextid%3DWA-UNK-UNK-UNK-AN_GK0T-GK1C%26mibextid%3D2Rb1fB%26ref%3Dwatch_permalink%26v%3D317653720813798%5C%22%3EAsk%20Me%20Anything%20(AMA)%20session%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Facebook%20today%20that%20no%20market%20will%20be%20closed%2C%20but%20movement%20in%20those%20present%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20area%20will%20be%20regulated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20theatres%20and%20restaurants%20be%20closed%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20said%20all%20theatres%20and%20restaurants%20in%20the%20controlled%20area%20of%20New%20Delhi%20district%20will%20remain%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20people%20use%20delivery%20services%20during%20the%20G20%20summit%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20arrangements%20made%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%2C%20cloud%20kitchens%20and%20other%20delivery%20services%20won't%20be%20allowed%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20area%20during%20the%20summit%20period.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20clarify%20that%20grocery%2C%20ATMs%20and%20medical%20stores%20(essential%20services)%2C%20and%20other%20establishments%20will%20remain%20open%2C%20even%20in%20the%20regulated%20zone%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20traffic%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%205-star%20hotels%20in%20Delhi%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20said%20that%20some%20heads%20of%20state%20will%20stay%20at%20Maurya%20Sheraton%20hotel%20in%20Saket%2C%20Lodhi%20hotel%20in%20Southwest%20district%20and%20Hyatt%20at%20Ring%20Road.%20%26quot%3BAll%20these%20are%20out%20of%20NDMC%20area%20and%20will%20function%20normally.%20Only%20on%20some%20occasions%2C%20when%20there%20wil