3BJawan%2C%26quot%3B%20directed%20by%20Atlee%2C%20is%20an%20action-packed%20film%20featuring%20Khan%2C%20Vijay%20Sethupathi%20as%20the%20antagonist%2C%20and%20Nayanthara%20as%20the%20female%20lead.%20Despite%20mixed%20reviews%20of%20the%20music%2C%20the%20film%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20a%20strong%20opening%20at%20the%20box%20office.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-gives-a-witty-reply-to-a-fan-who-asked-jawan-2-kab-aayega%2Farticleshow%2F103346431.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Weeks%20Before%20%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%26quot%3B%20Push%2C%20Centre%20Listed%20Pros%20And%20Cons%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWeeks%20before%20%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%26quot%3B%20got%20a%20fresh%20thrust%20with%20the%20government%20asking%20a%20panel%20to%20examine%20the%20proposal%2C%20Union%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Meghwal%20had%20listed%20the%20big%20hurdles%20and%20imperatives%20for%20syncing%20elections%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArjun%20Meghwal%20had%20cited%20five%20impediments%20to%20%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%26quot%3B%20and%20arguments%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20idea%20in%20a%20written%20reply%20in%20parliament%20on%2027%20July%2C%20to%20a%20question%20raised%20by%20Kirodi%20Lal%20Meena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHurdles%20Listed%20by%20Minister%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20move%20would%20require%20amendments%20in%20five%20articles%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20Law%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20These%20are%2C%20Article%2083%20on%20the%20duration%20of%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%2C%20Article%2085%20on%20the%20dissolution%20of%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0Lok%20Sabha%20by%20the%20President%2C%20Article%20172%20on%20the%20duration%20of%20state%20legislatures%2C%20Article%20174%20on%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0dissolving%20state%20legislatures%20and%20Article%20356%20on%20President's%20Rule%20in%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESimultaneous%20national%20and%20general%20elections%20will%20also%20require%20the%20consensus%20of%20all%20political%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMr%20Meghwal%20said%20given%20the%20country's%20federal%20structure%2C%20it%20was%20imperative%20that%20the%20consensus%20of%20all%20state%20governments%20was%20obtained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20cost%20of%20the%20move%20could%20run%20into%20thousands%20of%20crores%20as%20additional%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20and%20Voter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(EVMs%2FVVPATs)%20would%20be%20needed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BConsidering%20that%20the%20life%20of%20the%20(EVM)%20machine%20is%20only%2015%20years%2C%20this%20would%20imply%20that%20the%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20machine%20would%20be%20used%20for%20about%20three%20or%20four%20times%20in%20its%20life%20span%2C%20entailing%20huge%20expenditure%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20in%20its%20replacement%20every%2015%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Meghwal's%20reply.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20minister%20also%20listed%20the%20requirement%20of%20additional%20polling%20personnel%20and%20security%20forces.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%20listed%20by%20Law%20Minister%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESimultaneous%20elections%20will%20be%20a%20huge%20saving%20for%20the%20public%20exchequer.%20The%20minister%20says%20avoiding%20replicating%20the%20administrative%20and%20law%20and%20order%20machinery%20with%20repeated%20elections%20will%20also%20save%20the%20costs%20to%20political%20parties%20and%20candidates%20in%20their%20election%20campaigns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBecause%20of%20asynchronous%20national%20and%20state%20elections%2C%20including%20byelections%2C%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20is%20in%20force%20for%20prolonged%20periods%2C%20which%20impacts%20developmental%20and%20welfare%20programmes%20adversely.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20minister%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20South%20Africa%2C%20where%20elections%20to%20national%20and%20provincial%20legislatures%20are%20held%20simultaneously%20for%20five%20years%20and%20municipal%20elections%20are%20held%20two%20years%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20Sweden%2C%20the%20election%20to%20the%20national%20legislature%20(Riksdag)%20and%20provincial%20legislature%2Fcounty%20council%20(Landsting)%20and%20local%20bodies%2Fmunicipal%20assemblies%20(Kommunfullmaktige)%20are%20held%20on%20a%20fixed%20date%20-%20the%20second%20Sunday%20of%20September%20-%20for%20four%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20UK%2C%20the%20term%20of%20parliament%20is%20governed%20by%20the%20Fixed-term%20Parliament%20Act%2C%202011.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20committee%20led%20by%20former%20president%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20has%20been%20tasked%20with%20exploring%20simultaneous%20polls%20in%20India%2C%20which%20was%20the%20norm%20till%20the%201960s.%20India%20voted%20simultaneously%20for%20the%20Centre%20and%20states%20in%201952%2C%201957%2C%201962%20and%201967.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20to%20revert%20to%20simultaneous%20polls%20was%20suggested%20in%20the%20annual%20report%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20in%201983.%20Later%2C%20a%20Law%20Commission%20report%20referred%20to%20it%20in%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20BJP-led%20government%20came%20to%20power%2C%20the%20party%20made%20a%20strong%20pitch%20for%20%26quot%3Bone%20nation%2C%20one%20election%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693809240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-10%2Finfn4euk_bihar-election-2020-phase-1-voting-pti-photo_625x300_28_October_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fweeks-before-one-nation-one-election-push-centre-listed-pros-and-cons-4357272%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Weeks%20before%20%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%26quot%3B%20got%20a%20fresh%20thrust%20with%20the%20government%20asking%20a%20panel%20to%20examine%20the%20proposal%2C%20Union%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Meghwal%20had%20listed%20the%20big%20hurdles%20and%20imperatives%20for%20syncing%20elections%20nationwide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fweeks-before-one-nation-one-election-push-centre-listed-pros-and-cons-4357272%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fweeks-before-one-nation-one-election-push-centre-listed-pros-and-cons-4357272%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fweeks-before-one-nation-one-election-push-centre-listed-pros-and-cons-4357272%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woody%20Allen%20Considers%20Retirement%20After%20Latest%20Film%2C%20Still%20Maintains%20Innocence%20and%20Calls%20Cancel%20Culture%20%E2%80%98Silly%E2%80%99%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693809000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FGettyImages-1656611128.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235712494%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Woody%20Allen%20returned%20to%20the%20Venice%20Film%20Festival%20this%20weekend%20for%20the%20world%20premiere%20of%20%E2%80%9CCoup%20de%20Chance%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20romantic%20thriller%20that%20marks%20his%2050th%2C%20a