0push%20the%20ex-president's%20federal%20election%20interference%20trial%20to%20April%202026%2C%20they%20cited%20the%20landmark%20Supreme%20Court%20case%20regarding%20the%20infamous%20convictions%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BScottsboro%20Boys%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20nine%20young%20Black%20men%20falsly%20accused%20of%20raping%20two%20white%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22null%5C%22%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EIn%20the%201932%20decision%2C%20Powell%20v.%20Alabama%2C%C2%A0the%20court's%20ruling%20guaranteed%20the%20right%20of%20a%20defendant%20to%20%26quot%3Breasonable%20time%20and%20opportunity%20to%20secure%20counsel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22null%5C%22%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EThe%20Scottsboro%20case%20attracted%20widespread%20attention.%20The%20men%20were%20swiftly%20arrested%2C%20tried%2C%20and%20sentenced%20within%20weeks%2C%20with%20hardly%20had%20any%20opportunity%20to%20speak%20with%20their%20attorneys%20before%20their%20convictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22null%5C%22%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20Powell%2C%20the%20men%20had%20their%20convictions%20reversed%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20accusations%20didn't%20go%20away.%20Collectively%2C%20the%20men%20had%20spent%20decades%20in%20prison.%20By%201950%2C%20some%20battled%20declining%20health%20and%20violence.%20One%20of%20the%20men%20died%20by%20suicide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22null%5C%22%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3ETrump's%20legal%20team%2C%20in%20seeking%20to%20fight%20charges%20that%20Trump%20sought%20to%20subvert%20the%202020%20presidential%20election%20results%2C%20argued%20that%20that%20the%20former%20president%20needed%20additional%20time%20to%20prepare%20a%20defense%2C%20pointing%20to%20%3Cem%3EPowell.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22null%5C