to%20the%20holding%20and%20the%20legal%20principles%20that%20are%20set%20forth%20in%20Powell%20v.%20Alabama%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20didn't%20do%20in%20any%20way%20in%20our%20briefing%20was%20suggest%20that%20there%20are%20any%20parallels%20back%20to%20the%20factual%20circumstances%20of%20the%20Powell%20case%20with%20President%20Trump's%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-federal-election-interference-scottsboro-boys-2020-presidential-race-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693774319000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f4edb81b7ced0019c79bde%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-federal-election-interference-scottsboro-boys-2020-presidential-race-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22District%20Judge%20Tanya%20Chutkan%20rejected%20the%20Trump%20legal%20team's%20arguments%20for%20more%20time%2C%20and%20set%20the%20federal%20election%20interference%20trial%20for%20March%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(John%20L.%20Dorman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A68%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-federal-election-interference-scottsboro-boys-2020-presidential-race-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Heavy%20rain%20batters%20parts%20of%20Spain%20as%20residents%20urged%20to%20stay%20indoors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693774260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F70x70%2Fskynews-spain-weather_6273887.jpg%3F20230903211534%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fheavy-rain-batters-parts-of-spain-as-mayor-urges-residents-to-stay-indoors-12954602%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Railway%20lines%20have%20been%20closed%2C%20a%20football%20match%20has%20been%20cancelled%20and%20people%20have%