0human%20lineage%20evolved%20from%20%E2%80%94%20into%20Europe%20and%20Asia%20and%20evolved%20into%20the%20Neanderthals%20and%20the%20Denisovans%2C%20the%20Times%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArcheologist%20Nick%20Ashton%20told%20the%20Times%20that%20scientists%20have%20found%20human%20remains%20outside%20of%20Africa%20from%20the%20same%20period%20as%20the%20bottleneck%2C%20suggesting%20that%20a%20global%20disaster%20%26quot%3Bonly%20affected%20a%20limited%20population%2C%20who%20may%20have%20been%20ancestors%20of%20modern%20humans.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhuman-ancestors-almost-extinct-930000-years-ago-study-suggests-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693764177000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f4bf9b781926001910b4bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhuman-ancestors-almost-extinct-930000-years-ago-study-suggests-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Almost%20a%20million%20years%20later%2C%20that%20tiny%20group%20of%20human%20ancestors%20has%20now%20grown%20to%208%20billion%20people%20worldwide%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbalevic%40insider.com%20(Katie%20Balevic)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A203%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhuman-ancestors-almost-extinct-930000-years-ago-study-suggests-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Confident%20of%20meeting%20fiscal%20deficit%2C%20nominal%20GDP%20targets%3A%20DEA%20secy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693763362000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-09%2F03%2Ffull%2F1693763291-6364.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fgovt-confident-of-achieving-nominal-gdp-growth-targets-