2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F642332f2a5d9720019ef3702%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221356%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENick%20Veasey%2FScience%20Photo%20Library%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAn%20ape%20skull%20found%20in%20Turkey%20may%20challenge%20the%20belief%20that%20human%20and%20ape%20ancestors%20came%20from%20Africa.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20discovery%20suggests%20that%20hominins%20may%20have%20first%20evolved%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENot%20all%20scientists%20are%20convinced%20by%20the%20theory%2C%20however.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20of%20an%20ancient%20ape%20skull%20may%20challenge%20the%20long-held%20belief%20that%20the%20ancestors%20of%20apes%20and%20humans%20came%20from%20Africa%2C%20a%20controversial%20new%20study%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20partial%20skull%20of%20the%20ape%2C%20called%20an%20Anadoluvius%20turkae%2C%20was%20found%20in%20Cankiri%2C%20Turkey%2C%20and%20appears%20to%20date%20back%20to%208.7%20million%20years%20ago%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livescience.com%2Farchaeology%2Fhuman-and-ape-ancestors-arose-in-europe-not-in-africa-controversial-study-claims%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELive%20Science%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20early%20hominins%2C%20which%20include%20humans%2C%20the%20African%20apes%2C%20and%20their%20fossil%20ancestors%2C%20are%20not%20seen%20in%20Africa%20until%20around%20seven%20million%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20challenges%20the%20widely-held%20view%20that%20the%20ancestors%20of%20African%20apes%20and%20humans%20originated%20exclusively%20in%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20say%20that%20this%20suggests%20that%20hominins%20might%20have%20first%20evolved%20in%20Europe%20before%20migrating%20to%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221110%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20skull%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f4b6c5781926001910b37c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22740%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20skull.%3Cp%3ESevim-Erol%2C%20A.%2C%20Begun%2C%20D.R.%2C%20S%C3%B6zer%2C%20%C3%87.S.%20et%20al.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20findings%20further%20suggest%20that%20hominins%20not%20only%20evolved%20in%20western%20and%20central%20Europe%20but%20spent%20over%20five%20million%20years%20evolving%20there%20and%20spreading%20to%20the%20eastern%20Mediterranean%20before%20eventually%20dispersing%20into%20Africa%2C%20probably%20as%20a%20consequence%20of%20changing%20environments%20and%20diminishing%20forests%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Professor%20David%20Begun%2C%20a%20paleoanthropologist%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Toronto%20and%20co-senior%20author%20of%20the%20study%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fnews%2F2023%2F09%2F03%2Fdiscovery-of-87m-year-old-ape-rewrites-story-of-humanity%2F%3Fli_source%3DLI%26li_medium%3Dliftigniter-rhr%5C%22%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20new%20evidence%20supports%20the%20hypothesis%20that%20hominins%20originated%20in%20Europe%20and%20dispersed%20into%20Africa%20along%20with%20many%20other%20mammals%20between%20nine%20and%20seven%20million%20years%20ago%2C%20though%20it%20does%20not%20definitively%20prove%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20prove%20this%2C%20more%20fossils%20from%20Europe%20and%20Africa%20would%20need%20to%20be%20found%20from%20between%20seven%20and%20eight%20million%20years%20ago%20to%20try%20and%20find%20a%20link%20between%20the%20two%20groups%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20finding%20suggested%20that%20the%20ape%20would%20have%20weighed%20around%20110%20to%20130%20pounds%2C%20possibly%20lived%20in%20a%20dry%20forest%2C%20and%20likely%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20skull%20was%20found%20in%202015%20but%20its%20significance%20was%20discussed%20in%20research%20recently%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20Communications%20Biology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20researchers%20have%20said%20that%20the%20findings%20do%20not%20challenge%20our%20understanding%20of%20the%20origins%20of%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20been%20a%20long-running%20debate%20regarding%20great%20ape%20and%20our%20origins%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Professor%20Chris%20Stringer%2C%20research%20leader%20in%20human%20evolution%20at%20the%20Natural%20History%20Museum%20in%20London%2C%20The%20Telegraph%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20this%20find%20changes%20much%20from%20the%20discussions%20(in%20a%20recent%20paper%20in%20the%20journal%20Science)%20which%20concluded%3A%20'Current%20evidence%20suggests%20that%20hominins%20originated%20in%20Africa%20from%20Miocene%20ape%20ancestors%20unlike%20any%20living%20species.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fancient-ape-skull-human-origins-europe-africa-turkey-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693759186000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f4a45d1b7ced0019c78eee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fancient-ape-skull-human-origins-europe-africa-turkey-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20partial%20skull%20of%20the%20ape%2C%20which%20is%20called%20an%20Anadoluvius%20turkae%2C%20was%20found%20in%20Cankiri%2C%20northern%20Turkey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ashoaib%40insider.com%20(Alia%20Shoaib)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A260%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fancient-ape-skull-human-origins-europe-africa-turkey-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Florida%20judge%20struck%20down%20a%20DeSantis-drawn%20congressional%20map%20because%20it%20diminished%20the%20voting%20power%20of%20Black%20residents%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ron%20DeSantis%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f4a5d31b7ced0019c78f41%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Florida%20judge%20struck%20down%20the%20North%20Florida%20congressional%20map%20crafted%20last%20year%20by%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FCharlie%20Neibergall%2C%20File%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20Florida%20judge%20has%20tossed%20the%20North%20Florida%20redistricting%20plan%20engineered%20by%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJudge%20J.%20Lee%20Marsh%20ruled%20that%20DeSantis'%20congressional%20map%20violated%20the%20state%20constitution.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20contingent%20of%20voting%20rights%20groups%20and%20ex-Democratic%20Rep.%20Al%20Lawson%20praised%20the%20judge's%20decision.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Florida%20judge%20on%20Saturday%20struck%20down%20a%20congressional%20map%20crafted%20by%20Republican%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20lines%20violated%20the%20state's%20anti-gerrymandering%20protections%20and%20diminished%20the%20voting%20strength%20of%20Black%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ruling%2C%20Second%20Judicial%20Circuit%20Judge%20J.%20Lee%20Marsh%20ruled%20that%20the%20North%20Florida%20lines%20endorsed%20by%20DeSantis%20went%20against%20the%20state%20constitution's%20Fair%20Districts%20Amendment%20by%20%26quot%3Bdismantling%20a%20congressional%20district%20that%20enabled%20Black%20voters%20to%20elect%20their%20candidates%20of%20choice%20under%20the%20previous%20plan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-content-child-index%3D%5C%220-2%5C%22%3EUnder%20the%20Fair%20Districts%20provision%20approved%20by%20voters%2C%20districts%20can't%20be%20formulated%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20would%20%26quot%3Bdiminish%26quot%3B%20the%20opportunity%20for%20minority%20voters%20to%20select%20a%20candidate%20of%20their%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-content-child-index%3D%5C%220-2%5C%22%3EBut%20when%20DeSantis%20submitted%20his%20own%20map%20last%20year%20in%20lieu%20of%20the%20version%20that%20had%20been%20previously%20drawn%20by%20the%20GOP-controlled%20legislature%2C%20he%20tore%20apart%20then-Democratic%20Rep.%20Al%20Lawson's%205th%20Congressional%20District%2C%20which%20ran%20from%20areas%20west%20of%20Tallahassee%20to%20Jacksonville.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-content-child-index%3D%5C%220-2%5C%22%3EThe%20move%20created%20surrounding%20districts%20that%20were%20significantly%20more%20Republican.%20After%20the%20Florida%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F2022-election%2Fflorida-supreme-court-leaves-desantis-congressional-map-place-midterms-rcna31689%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%222d9a6b505c9d5ed42b702bd6adb0fb6c%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2240%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F2022-election%2Fflorida-supreme-court-leaves-desantis-congressional-map-place-midterms-rcna31689%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleft%20DeSantis'%20map%20in%20place%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%202022%20midterms%2C%20the%20GOP%20picked%20up%20four%20House%20seats%2C%20giving%20them%20a%2020-8%20statewide%20edge%20in%20the%20state's%20congressional%20delegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-content-child-index%3D%5C%220-2%5C%22%3EDeSantis%20said%20that%20Lawson's%20plurality-Black%20district%20as%20drawn%20was%20unconstitutional%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20was%20an%20illegal%20racial%20gerrymander.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20judge%20rejected%20that%20argument%2C%20which%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdesantis-democratic-congressional-district-restored-agreement-black-voters-gop-lawson-2023-8%5C%22%3Epaves%20the%20way%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20restoration%20of%20Lawson's%20district%20or%20the%20creation%20of%20one%20with%20a%20similar%20configuration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlorida%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Cord%20Byrd%20said%20in%20a%20text%20message%20that%20he%20disagreed%20with%20the%20judge's%20decision%20and%20would%20appeal%20the%20ruling%20to%20the%20state%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F09%2F02%2Fjudge-says-desantis-congressional-map-is-unconstitutional-orders-lawmakers-to-draw-new-one-00113835%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Politico%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20contingent%20of%20groups%2C%20including%20Black%20Voters%20Matter%2C%20Equal%20Ground%2C%20Florida%20Rising%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flwvfl.org%2Fstate-of-florida-admits-diminishment-of-black-voting-power-in-redistricting-case-agrees-to-path-for-new-remedial-map-for-2024%2F%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22964c1a325d7f685dfed27af31e2471ea%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2280%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flwvfl.org%2Fstate-of-florida-admits-diminishment-of-black-voting-power-in-redistricting-case-agrees-to-path-for-new-remedial-map-for-2024%2F%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELeague%20of%20Women%20Voters%20of%20Florida%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0sued%20the%20state%20over%20the%20congressional%20maps%20one%20day%20after%20DeSantis%20signed%20them%20into%20law.%20They%20alleged%20he%20had%20used%20the%20bully%20pulpit%20of%20his%20office%20to%20push%20legislative%20Republicans%20into%20accepting%20his%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJasmine%20Burney-Clark%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Equal%20Ground%2C%20pointed%20to%20the%20judge's%20decision%20as%20one%20that%20would%20restore%20the%20voting%20power%20of%20Black%20Floridians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVoters%20should%20be%20empowered%20to%20pick%20their%20leaders%2C%20not%20the%20other%20way%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Saturday.%20%26quot%3BWe%20applaud%20the%20judge's%20ruling%20recognizing%20the%20need%20to%20restore%20the%20voting%20power%20of%20Black%20Floridians%20in%20North%20Florida%2C%20and%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20map%20that%20empowers%20voters%20in%20that%20region%20to%20select%20a%20candidate%20of%20their%20choice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20state%20and%20the%20aforementioned%20voting%20rights%20groups%20are%20set%20to%20ask%20that%20the%20Florida%20Supreme%20Court%20take%20up%20the%20case%20directly%2C%20which%20would%20allow%20them%20to%20bypass%20the%20regular%20process%20that%20would%20involve%20a%20lower%20appellate%20court.%20And%20they%20are%20also%20poised%20to%20put%20forward%20a%20schedule%20that%20would%20allow%20the%20Florida%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20make%20a%20decision%20by%20Dec.%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Florida%20legislature%20will%20have%20the%20first%20opportunity%20to%20construct%20a%20new%20map%2C%20which%20the%20plaintiffs%20may%20challenge.%20But%20if%20the%20legislature%20doesn't%20draw%20a%20new%20map%2C%20both%20sides%20would%20likely%20sign%20off%20on%20a%20district%20stretching%20from%20Duval%20County%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20government%20is%20consolidated%20with%20Jacksonville%20%E2%80%94%20to%20majority-Black%20Gadsden%20County.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawson%2C%20who%20ran%20for%20reelection%20in%202022%20and%20lost%20to%20Republican%20Rep.%20Neal%20Dunn%20in%20the%20conservative%202nd%20congressional%20district%2C%20praised%20the%20judge's%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20pleased%20the%20Court%20struck%20down%20the%20DeSantis%20congressional%20map%2C%20finding%20that%20his%20office%20and%20the%20Legislature%20violated%20the%20Constitution.%20This%20decision%20is%20a%20victory%20for%20the%20people%20of%20North%20Florida%2C%20particularly%20those%20communities%20of%20color%20who%20have%20been%20historically%20disenfranchised%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20still%20more%20work%20to