d%20was%20angry%20over%20her%20living%20with%20another%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20woman%20was%20earlier%20married%20to%20another%20man.%20Thereafter%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20custom%20of%20%3Cem%3Enata%20pratha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20she%20started%20living%20with%20a%20second%20man%2C%20who%20is%20now%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20the%20case.%20He%20was%20enraged%20after%20she%20started%20living%20with%20another%20%5Ba%20third%5D%20man%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENata%20pratha%3C%2Fem%3E%20roughly%20translates%20from%20Hindi%20to%20%E2%80%98custom%20of%20relations%E2%80%99.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fhindi%2Farticles%2Fcnde2pj167zo%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBBC%20Hindi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20custom%20is%20prevalent%20among%20some%20of%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20communities%20and%20may%20involve%20married%20women%20living%20with%20men%20other%20than%20their%20husbands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBudhaniya%20told%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20woman%E2%80%99s%20husband%2C%20%E2%80%9Calong%20with%20his%20associates%2C%20reached%20the%20place%20where%20%5Bshe%5D%20was%20staying%20and%20abducted%20her%2C%20before%20she%20was%20stripped%20and%20paraded.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20father%20told%20reporters%20on%20Saturday%20(September%202)%20that%20the%20accused%20also%20beat%20his%20daughter%20up%2C%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%2C%20adding%20she%20is%20four%20or%20five%20months%20pregnant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%20Hindi%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20one%20of%20the%20accused%20filmed%20the%20video%20in%20Pratapgarh%E2%80%99s%20Dhariyavad%20village%20and%20uploaded%20it%20to%20the%20internet%20after%20travelling%20to%20a%20place%20with%20connectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20report%20also%20said%20that%20local%20police%20formed%2030%20teams%20to%20investigate%20the%20incident.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%2