s%2Fworld-middle-east-66700307.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Scared%20to%20Buy%2C%20Eat%20Meat%E2%80%99%3A%20Muslims%20in%20Mathura%20After%20Arrests%20on%20Suspicion%20of%20Cow%20Slaughter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03160038%2Fimage-1275.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMathura%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOn%20September%2011%2C%202022%2C%20Sameer%20A.%2C%20owner%20of%20a%20printing%20press%2C%20discovered%20some%20bags%20lying%20outside%20the%20main%20gate%20of%20his%20house%20in%20Mathura.%20As%20he%20opened%20the%20bags%2C%20he%20was%20shocked%20to%20find%20the%20bags%20containing%20pieces%20of%20buffalo%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Mathura%20Police%20was%20informed%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20Sameer%20was%20arrested%2C%20and%20sent%20to%20jail%20for%2056%20days%20on%20charges%20of%20%E2%80%98cow%20slaughter%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Futtar-pradesh-govt-clears-ordinance-to-prevent-cow-slaughter%2Farticle31792688.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTo%2520protect%2520cows%2520and%2520prevent%2Cup%2520to%2520%25E2%2582%25B95%2520lakh.%5C%22%3Ea%20crime%20punishable%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20imprisonment%20of%20up%20to%2010%20years%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2031%2C%202021%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20banned%20the%20sale%20of%20meat%20and%20liquor%20in%2022%20municipal%20wards%20of%20Mathura%20that%20come%20within%20a%201.5%20kilometre%20radius%20of%20the%20Shri%20Krishna%20Janmasthan%20Temple%20%E2%80%93%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Krishna.%20In%202017%2C%20Adityanath%20had%20placed%20a%20similar%20ban%20in%20areas%20religious%20areas%20significant%20to%20Hinduism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20many%20Muslims%20in%20Mathura%20have%20shared%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20they%20have%20faced%20cases%20where%20the%20police%20have%20even%20arrested%20some%20of%20them%20on%20%E2%80%98suspicion%E2%80%99%20of%20cow%20slaughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20case%20of%20same%20story%2C%20copied%20FIRs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereviewed%20seven%20FIRs%20filed%20in%202022%20across%20various%20police%20stations%20in%20Mathura%2C%20including%20Kotwali%2C%20Highway%2C%20Sadar%20Bazaar%2C%20and%20Govind%20Nagar.%20It%20found%20that%20these%20FIRs%20were%20mere%20copies%20of%20each%20other%20with%20names%20and%20dates%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20FIR%200345%2C%20filed%20on%20August%2031%2C%202022%20at%20Govind%20Nagar%20police%20station%2C%20says%20that%20the%20police%20received%20a%20tip%20from%20an%20informer%20that%20a%20woman%20and%20a%20man%20were%20transporting%2C%20rather%20allegedly%20smuggling%2C%2043%20kilograms%20of%20cow%20meat%20on%20foot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20FIR%200584%2C%20filed%20on%20September%2012%2C%202022%20at%20Kotwali%20police%20station%2C%20says%20that%20the%20police%20were%20tipped%20off%20by%20an%20informer%20that%2025%20kgs%20of%20cow%20meat%20was%20found%20in%2025%20packets%20outside%20a%20Muslim%20man%E2%80%99s%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20again%2C%20FIR%200388%2C%20filed%20on%20June%2025%2C%202022%20at%20Kotwali%20police%20station%2C%20says%20that%20the%20police%20received%20a%20tip%20from%20an%20informer%20that%20two%20men%20and%20a%20woman%20were%20smuggling%206.4%20kgs%20of%20cow%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20on%20March%209%2C%20upon%20receiving%20a%20tip-off%20from%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Egaurakshaks%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20(cow%20vigilantes)%2C%20the%20police%20claimed%20to%20have%20seized%20five%20quintals%20of%20meat%2C%20suspected%20to%20be%20beef%2C%20from%20a%20vehicle.%20Notably%2C%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20the%20police%20arrived%20with%20the%20cow%20vigilantes%2C%20and%20an%20arrest%20was%20made%20solely%20on%20suspicion%2C%20even%20before%20the%20meat%20was%20tested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2030%2C%20the%20Govind%20Nagar%20police%20received%20a%20tip%20from%20informers%20to%20arrest%20a%20Muslim%20man%20for%20selling%20around%2020%20kgs%20of%20alleged%20cow%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdelhi-police-affidavit-shows-muslims-bore-brunt-of-riots-silent-on-who-targeted-them-and-why%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Police%20Affidavit%20Shows%20Muslims%20Bore%20Brunt%20of%20Riots%2C%20Silent%20on%20Who%20Targeted%20Them%20and%20Why%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20police%20officers%20stationed%20at%20Kotwali%20and%20Govind%20Nagar%20police%20stations.%20The%20officers%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20with%20have%20handled%20cases%20involving%20alleged%20cow%20slaughter.%20According%20to%20them%2C%20all%20actions%20taken%20by%20the%20UP%20Police%20in%20these%20matters%20strictly%20adhere%20to%20the%20law.%20They%20said%20there%20is%20no%20activity%20that%20is%20transcending%20the%20limits%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20that%20informers%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20apprehending%20those%20who%20violate%20the%20no-meat%20law%20near%20the%20Krishna%20Janmasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspector%20Sanjay%20Kumar%2C%20based%20at%20PS%20Kotwali%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20law%20aimed%20at%20preventing%20cow%20slaughter%20is%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20society%2C%20and%20that%20convictions%20must%20be%20made%20within%20the%20framework%20of%20the%20law.%20Furthermore%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20tried%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20DM%20Mathura%2C%20but%20received%20no%20response%20to%20the%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJailed%20over%20suspicion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%2056%20days%2C%20Sameer%20was%20released%20from%20jail%20in%20early%20November%20last%20year.%20The%20days%20he%20spent%20in%20jail%20over%20suspicion%20of%20cow%20slaughtering%20changed%20him%20as%20a%20person.%20He%20is%20always%20reminded%20of%20the%20harassment%20he%20faced%20for%20belonging%20to%20a%20traditionally%20meat%20consuming%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20I%20returned%20from%20jail%2C%20I%20was%20even%20scared%20of%20asking%20for%20non-vegetarian%20food.%20I%20have%20always%20been%20fond%20of%20meat%20items%2C%20but%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20meat%20that%20was%20caught%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20mine%2C%20yet%20I%20had%20to%20spend%20so%20much%20time%20in%20jail.%20I%20am%20scared%20to%20eat%20meat%2C%20even%20going%20to%20shops%20to%20buy%20it%20is%20traumatic%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20person%2C%20arrested%20over%20the%20same%20charges%20as%20Sameer%2C%20Mohammed%20Saleem%2C%20spent%20three%20months%20in%20prison%20after%20informers%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20had%20cow%20meat.%20His%20elder%20brother%2C%20Sadiq%2C%20was%20also%20arrested%20over%20the%20same%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadiq%20said%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20share%20his%20pain%20with%20the%20media%2C%20because%20he%20was%20scared%20of%20getting%20arrested%20again%2C%20for%20expressing%20his%20side%20of%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalit%20Chauhan%2C%20a%20Mathura-based%20Congress%20leader%2C%20said%20that%20he%20fails%20to%20find%20any%20logic%20in%20the%20way%20this%20law%20is%20being%20used%20in%20the%20state.%20Chauhan%20said%20that%20the%20law%20is%20purely%20being%20deployed%20to%20harass%20and%20jail%20Muslims%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20ruining%20their%20existence%20as%20a%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20FIRs%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CJust%20take%20a%20cursory%20look%20at%20the%20FIRs.%20The%20police%20are%20grossly%20misusing%20this%20law%20against%20Muslims%20and%20Dalits%20across%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20not%20just%20Mathura.%20Knowing%20well%20that%20Muslims%20are%20a%20meat-eating%20community%2C%20they%20target%20them.%20Without%20even%20confirming%20whether%20the%20%E2%80%98caught%20meat%E2%80%99%20was%20at%20all%20of%20the%20cow%2C%20they%20jail%20Muslims.%20Procedurally%2C%20they%20need%20to%20assess%20the%20meat%20sample%20in%20a%20lab%2C%20only%20then%20can%20they%20pronounce%20a%20jail%20term%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEthnic%20cleansing%20and%20economic%20targeting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKale%20Khan%20Qureshi%2C%2072%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20and%20oldest%20restaurateurs%20in%20Mathura.%20Situated%20just%20meters%20away%20from%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Krishna%2C%20Qureshi%20had%20to%20shut%20his%20non-vegetarian%20restaurant%20in%202017.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20my%20restaurant%20in%201969.%20I%20watched%20it%20grow%20as%20I%20grew%20older.%20After%20the%20ban%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20reduced%20to%20selling%20tea%20at%20the%20restaurant%2C%20and%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20bring%20in%201%2F10th%20of%20what%20we%20used%20to%20earn.%20I%20had%20to%20let%20go%20of%20most%20of%20our%20staff%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03162329%2Fimage-1277.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03162329%2Fimage-1277.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03162329%2Fimage-1277-300x147.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03162329%2Fimage-1277-1024x502.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671278%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22588%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKale%20Khan%20Qureshi.%20Photo%3A%20Tarushi%20Aswani%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETabrez%20Qureshi%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20a%20slaughterhouse%20in%20Mathura%2C%20has%20been%20unemployed%20since%20the%20meat%20ban%20was%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20ban%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20reasonable%2C%20not%20because%20thousands%20like%20him%20have%20been%20pushed%20to%20poverty%2C%20but%20because%20meat%20is%20still%20meat%2C%20even%20when%20it%20is%20sold%20beyond%20the%20banned%2022%20wards.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20banned%20areas%20near%20the%20Janmasthan%20Temple%20complex%20are%20heavily%20dominated%20by%20Muslims.%20If%20they%20really%20care%20about%20the%20sanctity%20of%20Mathura%2C%20then%20what%20sense%20does%20the%2022-ward%20ban%20make%3F%20%5BThe%20government%5D%20should%20have%20banned%20it%20in%20all%2045%20wards.%20Why%20did%20it%20ban%20meat%20in%20nearby%20wards%2C%20dominated%20by%20Muslims%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03162052%2Fimage-1276.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03162052%2Fimage-1276.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03162052%2Fimage-1276-300x143.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03162052%2Fimage-1276-1024x487.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671277%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22571%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20the%20empty%20slaughterhouse%20which%20was%20shut%20in%202021.%20Photo%3A%20Tarushi%20Aswani%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Vijay%20Bhargava%2C%20public%20relations%20officer%2C%20Shri%20Krishna%20Janmasthan%20Temple%2C%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20is%20bringing%20back%20%E2%80%9Cpurity%E2%80%9D%20in%20Mathura.%C2%A0In%20an%20exclusive%20conversation%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Bhargava%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNon-Muslims%20cannot%20enter%20Mecca%2C%20then%20they%20should%20understand%20when%20we%20take%20such%20steps%20in%20our%20place%20of%20worship%2C%20yet%20injustice%20is%20being%20meted%20out%20to%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20why%20mostly%20Muslim-dominated%20areas%20have%20been%20included%20under%20this%20ban%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20your%20beliefs%20are%20Islamic%2C%20then%20why%20are%20you%20living%20in%20Mathura%3F%20If%20you%20want%20to%20strictly%20follow%20Islam%2C%20you%20can%20practice%20it%20elsewhere%20or%20outside%20Mathura.%20Yogi%20ji%20has%20validated%20our%20Hindu%20scriptures%20with%20this%20meat%20ban.%20India%20is%20aggressively%20moving%20towards%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%20Those%20selling%20cow%20meat%20should%20be%20awarded%20a%20death%20sentence.%20India%20was%20partitioned%20in%20the%20past%20wrongly%2C%20but%20if%20it%20was%20partitioned%20over%20religion%2C%20people%20should%20have%20followed%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Eabout%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20ban%2C%20Mehraj%20Alam%2C%20a%20BAMCEF%20(Backward%20and%20Minority%20Communities%20Employees%20Federation)%20worker%2C%20said%20that%20the%20ban%20has%20not%20only%20affected%20the%20butchers%20or%20the%20sellers%20or%20the%20restaurant%20owners%2C%20it%20has%20had%20an%20impact%20on%20a%20whole%20chain%20of%20people%20employed%20with%20these%20people.%20Even%C2%A0carcass%20and%20bone%20dealers%E2%80%99%20livelihoods%20have%20been%20impacted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlam%20claims%20that%20at%20least%205%2C000%20Muslims%20have%20been%20affected%20by%20the%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShakir%20Hussain%2C%20another%20restaurateur%20affected%20by%20the%20ban%2C%20said%20that%20the%20whole%20idea%20behind%20the%20ban%2C%20and%20the%20cases%20on%20cow%20slaughter%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20aimed%20at%20only%20one%20objective%3A%20cleansing%20Mathura%20of%20Muslims.%20%E2%80%9CHundreds%20of%20Muslims%20have%20already%20left%20Mathura%20since%20the%20ban.%20They%20are%20traditionally%20meat%20slaughtering%20communities%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20any%20other%20skill%2C%20hence%20to%20survive%2C%20they%20left%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693740645000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03160038%2Fimage-1275.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fscared-to-buy-eat-meat-muslims-in-mathura-after-arrests-on-suspicion-of-cow-slaughter%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20reviewing%20seven%20FIRs%20filed%20in%202022%20across%20various%20police%20stations%20in%20Mathura%2C%20'The%20Wire'%20found%20that%20these%20were%20mere%20copies%20of%20each%20other%20with%20names%20and%20dates%20changed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fscared-to-buy-eat-meat-muslims-in-mathura-after-arrests-on-suspicion-of-cow-slaughter%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20plans%20to%20deport%20all%20African%20migrants%20from%20Israel%20after%20Eritrean%20groups%20involved%20in%20violent%20clashes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693740600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F70x70%2Fskynews-israel-protest_6273052.jpg%3F20230903125217%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbenjamin-netanyahu-says-he-wants-all-eritrean-migrants-involved-in-israel-clashes-deported-12953989%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Plans%20should%20be%20drawn%20up%20to%20remove%20all%20African%20migrants%20from%20Israel%20after%20groups%20of%20Eritreans%20were%20involved%20in%20a%20violent%20clash%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjam