0your%20phone%20on%20power%20saving%20mode%20till%20a%20charging%20cord%20is%20available.%20The%20charging%20cord%20for%20the%20lander%20and%20rover%20will%20be%20sunrise%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20lunar%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20different%20ISRO%20scientist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Ftechnology%2Fscience%2Fchandrayaan-3-pragyan-rover-isro-updates-8921530%2F%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Sun%20does%20rise%20over%20Pragyan%2C%20there%20is%20a%20chance%20it%20may%20resume%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHoping%20for%20a%20successful%20awakening%20for%20another%20set%20of%20assignments!%20Else%2C%20it%20will%20forever%20stay%20there%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20lunar%20ambassador%2C%E2%80%9D%20ISRO%20said%20on%20X%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693735820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02120229%2FScreenshot-2023-09-02-at-11.50.25-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fspace%2Faditya-l1-performs-first-earthbound-manoeuvre%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20manoeuvres%20are%20intended%20to%20help%20the%20spacecraft%20gain%20the%20necessary%20velocity%20to%20travel%20towards%20the%20Sun.%20ISRO%20announced%20that%20the%20next%20such%20manoeuvre%20is%20scheduled%20for%20Tuesday%20(September%205).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fspace%2Faditya-l1-performs-first-earthbound-manoeuvre%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20set%20to%20get%20over%20%C2%A3110%2C000%20in%20compensation%20after%20great-grandfather%20hanged%20by%20Nazis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693734000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F768x432%2Fskynews-mauro-petrarca-hanged_6272968.jpg%3F20230903105648%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fworld-war-two-italian-man-set-to-get-over-163110000-in-compensation-after-great-grandfather-hanged-by-nazi-troops-12953940%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Relatives%20of%20six%20Italian%20men%20hanged%20by%20German%20troops%20during%20World%20War%20Two%20are%20set%20to%20receive%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20euros%20in%20compensation%20for%20their%20families'%20trauma.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fworld-war-two-italian-man-set-to-get-over-110-000-in-compensation-after-great-grandfather-hanged-by-nazi-troops-12953940%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fworld-war-two-italian-man-set-to-get-over-110-000-in-compensation-after-great-grandfather-hanged-by-nazi-troops-12953940%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fworld-war-two-italian-man-set-to-get-over-110-000-in-compensation-after-great-grandfather-hanged-by-nazi-troops-12953940%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mason%20Greenwood's%20new%20manager%20says%20loan%20signing%20is%20'delicate%20issue'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693733700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-mason-greenwood-manchester-united_6254221.jpg%3F20230818053624%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmason-greenwoods-new-manager-says-loan-signing-is-delicate-issue-12953934%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mason%20Greenwood's%20new%20manager%20has%20said%20signing%20the%20player%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bdelicate%20issue%26quot%3B%20that%20is%20%26quot%3Bkind%20of%20a%20tough%20situation%20to%20talk%20about%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A819%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmason-greenwoods-new-manager-says-loan-signing-is-delicate-issue-12953934%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmason-greenwoods-new-manager-says-loan-signing-is-delicate-issue-12953934%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmason-greenwoods-new-manager-says-loan-signing-is-delicate-issue-12953934%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%3A%20A%20Poor%20Argument%20for%20Cost%20Savings%20and%20the%20Need%20for%20Increased%20Poll%20Spending%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16163914%2F2048px-BMC_Election_2012_-_Ink_mark_after_voting_6886404209.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ETrue%20to%20form%2C%20the%20Modi%202.0%20regime%20exposed%20both%20faces%20of%20its%20duplicitous%20nature%20with%20great%20speed.%20The%20magnanimous%20rhetoric%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20(similar%20to%201.0)%20was%20followed%20in%20short%20order%20by%20the%20heckling%20of%20several%20non-BJP%20MPs%20during%20their%20oath%20of%20office%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffresh-triple-talaq-bill-lok-sabha-opposition-protest%5C%22%3Etabling%20of%20the%20Triple%20Talaq%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20merger%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2F4-tdp-mps-join-bjp-rajya-sabha%5C%22%3ETDP%E2%80%99s%20under-investigation%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20most%20telling%2C%20the%20renewal%20of%20the%20call%20for%20%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20a%20piece%20with%20the%20deplorable%20and%20farcical%20breach%20of%20decorum%20and%20secularism%20during%20the%20swearing%20in%2C%20and%20the%20patent%20violation%20of%20the%20constitution%E2%80%99s%20equality%20clause%20in%20the%20penalty%20clause%20of%20the%20Triple%20Talaq%20Bill%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%E2%80%99%20proposal%20is%20profoundly%20unconstitutional%20%E2%80%93%20a%20clear%20violation%20of%20the%20Union%20of%20States%E2%80%99%20federalist%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20constitution.%20This%20has%20already%20been%20highlighted%20by%20many%2C%20who%20have%20also%20emphasised%20the%20structural%20and%20legal%20limitations%20of%20implementing%20synchronised%20five-year%20terms%2C%20starting%20with%20currently%20non-synchronised%20terms%20(for%20example%2C%20how%20would%20one%20extend%20or%20cut%20short%20an%20existing%20State%20Legislature%E2%80%99s%20term%20to%20enable%20the%20first%20synchronised%20election%2C%20within%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20constitution)%2C%20or%20managing%20the%20mid-term%20loss%20of%20a%20majority%20between%20elections%20(would%20one%20call%20for%20elections%20for%20the%20remaining%20part%20of%20the%20fixed%20five-year%20term%2C%20thereby%20doubling%20the%20costs%3B%20or%20continue%20with%20a%20government%20which%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20majority%20and%20hence%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20bills%20passed%20in%20the%20House%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20numbers%3F).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20the%20cost%20saving%20argument%20is%20poor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlleged%20benefits%20of%20such%20a%20move%2C%20such%20as%20cost%20savings%2C%20are%20easily%20dismissed%20by%20a%20simple%20analysis%20of%20the%20facts.%20Estimates%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20holding%20state%20elections%20vary%20from%20Rs%201%20crore%20per%20MLA%20(as%20stated%20in%20the%20recent%20Karnataka%20polls)%2C%20or%20around%20Rs%204%2C150%20crore%20every%20five%20years%20for%20all%20states%20combined%2C%20to%20about%20Rs%205%2C500%20crore%20at%20an%20aggregate%20level.%20While%20this%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20(albeit%20for%20the%20exercise%20of%20voter%E2%80%99s%20rights%20in%20a%20Constitutional%20Democracy)%2C%20it%20pales%20into%20insignificance%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20total%20budgets%20of%20all%20states%20over%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20Tamil%20Nadu%20as%20an%20example.%20It%20has%20234%20elected%20MLAs%2C%20so%20one%20can%20assume%20a%20cost%20of%20about%20Rs%20250%20crore%20(on%20the%20high%20side)%20as%20the%20cost%20of%20running%20the%20assembly%20elections%20every%20five%20years.%20Compare%20that%20cost%20%E2%80%93%20for%20the%20critical%20function%20of%20implementing%20democracy%20%E2%80%93%20to%20either%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20Budget%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20over%20the%20five-year%20term%20of%20the%20elected%20Legislature%2C%20which%20I%20conservatively%20estimate%20at%20around%20Rs%2013%20lakh%20crores%20for%20the%20(current)%2015th%20Legislative%20Assembly%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MLA%20Constituency%20Development%20Fund%20of%20Rs%202.50%20Crore%20per%20MLA%2C%20per%20year%2C%20or%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%202%2C925%20crore%20(0.23%25%20of%20the%20budget).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20once-in-five%20years%20Assembly%20Election%20costs%20under%200.02%25%20of%20the%20total%20money%20to%20be%20spent%20through%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20budgets%20approved%20by%20these%20very%20elected%20MLAs%20as%20required%20by%20the%20Constitution%2C%20and%20about%208%25%20of%20all%20MLAs%20Constituency%20Development%20Funds%20over%20the%20same%20five-year%20period.%20For%20most%20reasonable%20people%2C%20the%20argument%20of%20cost%20savings%20as%20a%20motivation%20for%20simultaneous%20elections%2C%20should%20end%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20on%20the%20topic%20of%20alleged%20cost%20savings%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20state%20and%20Central%20governments%20spend%20large%20amounts%20on%20questionable%20items%20(thousands%20of%20crores%20on%20statues%2C%20many%20thousands%20of%20crores%20on%20publicity)%2C%20and%20also%20end%20up%20underspending%20massive%20amounts%20of%20budgeted%20funds%20due%20to%20the%20inability%20to%20execute%20as%20planned%20(the%202016%20CAG%20report%20cited%20unused%20cess%20funds%20of%20over%20Rs%201%2C30%2C000%20crore%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20disaggregating%20the%20cost%20components%20of%20the%20election%20process%2C%20it%20is%20not%20even%20clear%20that%20simultaneous%20elections%20will%20lead%20to%20noticeable%20savings%20at%20all.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20has%20microscopically%20few%20full-time%20employees%20and%20relies%20massively%20on%20both%20ex-officio%20(for%20example%2C%20Collector%20is%20the%20Electoral%20Officer%20for%20the%20District)%20and%20a%20co-opted%20workforce%20(Local%20Body%20employees%20are%20assigned%20additional%20duties%20for%20voter%20list%20maintenance%20and%20polling).%20The%20costs%20of%20procuring%20and%20handling%20twice%20the%20number%20of%20EVMs%20on%20one%20day%20will%20not%20be%20much%20lower%20than%20handing%20half%20the%20machines%20on%20two%20different%20days%2C%20though%20the%20latter%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20more%20efficient%20and%20reliable.%20So%2C%20when%20comparing%20both%20fixed%20and%20variable%20costs%20of%20the%20actual%20election%20process%2C%20the%20prospects%20for%20cutting%20costs%20by%20moving%20to%20simultaneous%20elections%20seem%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20we%20need%20to%20spend%20more%20on%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cb%3Eelections%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20optimising%20public%2Fgovernment%20resources%20cannot%20provide%20justification%20for%20the%20notion%20of%20%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%E2%80%99%2C%20what%20about%20the%20spending%20of%20political%20parties%3F%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20spending%20of%20parties%20will%20be%20reduced%20by%20reducing%20the%20number%20of%20elections.%20But%20why%20should%20the%20very%20fabric%20of%20our%20constitution%20be%20shredded%20to%20reduce%20the%20spending%20of%20political%20parties%3F%20That%E2%80%99s%20as%20illogical%20as%20treating%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20disease%20by%20handcuffing%20the%20doctor!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20my%20participation%20in%20the%20election%20process%20as%20a%20candidate%2C%20as%20well%20as%20my%20observations%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20a%20wing%20in%20my%20party%20which%20focuses%20on%20data%20and%20processes%20amongst%20other%20things%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20argue%20that%20we%20need%20to%20spend%20substantially%20more%20on%20elections%20to%20ensure%20a%20true%20exercise%20in%20democracy%2C%20not%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20deep%20flaws%20in%20the%20basic%20processes%2C%20starting%20with%20many%20lacunae%20in%20the%20voter%20lists%20%E2%80%93%20of%20both%20omission%20and%20inclusion.%20A%20simple%20histogram%20of%20voters%20by%20age%20%E2%80%93%20which%20should%20slope%20from%20(left)%20youngest%20down%20to%20oldest%20(right)%20in%20a%20growing%20country%20like%20India%202%20will%20prove%20the%20under-enrollment%20(omission)%20of%2018%20to%2025-year-old%20voters.%20And%20for%20wrongful%20inclusion%2C%20one%20need%20to%20look%20no%20further%20than%20the%20R.K.%20Nagar%20bye-elections%20of%202017%2C%20where%20the%20State%20Election%20Commission%20deleted%20over%2047%2C000%20entries%20from%20the%20rolls%20of%20this%20single%20MLA%20constituency%20in%20two%20phases%20between%20April%202017%20(when%20the%20bye-poll%20was%20originally%20scheduled%20but%20later%20cancelled)%20to%20December%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20analysing%20the%20voter%20lists%20post%20those%20deletions%2C%20we%20found%20a%20few%20hundred%20more%20instances%20of%20duplicate%2Finexplicable%20entries%20%E2%80%93%20which%20we%20took%20to%20the%20CEO%20for%20rectification.%20In%20the%20most%20mindboggling%20instance%2C%20one%20voter%20ID%20was%20listed%20six%20times%20across%20five%20different%20booths%2C%20referencing%20a%2026-year-old%20female%20with%20the%20same%20Hindu%20name%20in%20all%20but%20one%20case%2C%20where%20the%20voter%20was%20listed%20as%20a%2043-year-old%20male%20with%20a%20Muslim%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyone%20with%20experience%20at%20polling%20booths%20on%20election%20day%20can%20attest%20to%20many%20further%20concerns.%20Neither%20the%20government%20employees%20assigned%20to%20election%20duty%20(Booth%20Officers)%2C%20nor%20the%20agents%20of%20most%20candidates%20(across%20all%20parties)%20are%20fully%20trained%20on%20the%20procedures%2C%20and%20especially%20on%20how%20to%20handle%20inadvertent%2C%20let%20alone%20malicious%2C%20breakdowns%20in%20the%20process%20(like%20mid-day%20EVM%20failure).%20We%20found%20that%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20booth%20officers%20had%20candidates%E2%80%99%20agents%20sign%20Form%2017Cs%20(Final%20count%20of%20polling%20to%20be%20declared%20after%20polling%20is%20completed)%2C%20without%20the%20details%20filled%20in%2C%20in%20the%20morning%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20is%20the%20massive%20disconnect%20between%20the%20EC%E2%80%99s%20data%2C%20reported%20on%20its%20own%20official%20forms%20and%20lists%2C%20at%20different%20stages%20of%20the%20election%20process.%20In%20the%20recent%20General%20Elections%2C%20we%20noted%20hundreds%20of%20instances%20of%20variation%20between%20the%20total-vote%20counts%20in%20the%20paper%20Form%2017C%2C%20and%20the%20EC%E2%80%99s%20summary%20sheet.%20In%20most%20cases%20it%20was%20of%20a%20few%20votes%20difference%20either%20way%20(%2B%2F-)%2C%20but%20in%20a%20few%20cases%20it%20was%20hundreds%20of%20votes.%20Thankfully%2C%20our%20MP%20was%20able%20to%20get%20many%20of%20the%20biggest%20discrepancies%20cleared%20up%20prior%20to%20counting%20%E2%80%93%20with%20many%20being%20retracted%20as%20clerical%2Ftyping%20error.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20perhaps%20worst%20of%20all%2C%20every%20General%20Election%20shows%20a%20big%20difference%2C%20in%20almost%20every%20constituency%2C%20between%20the%20EC%E2%80%99s%20own%20booth-wise%20data%20on%20votes%20polled%20on%20election%20day%20(Form%2017Cs)%2C%20compared%20to%20booth-wise%20votes%20counted%20on%20counting%20day%20(Form%2020s).%20Here%20also%20there%20are%20instances%20of%20both%20errors%3A%20more%20votes%20counted%20than%20polled%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20and%20more%20votes%20polled%20than%20counted%20in%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99m%20not%20(or%20at%20least%2C%20not%20yet)%20alleging%20any%20conspiracy%20in%20these%20discrepancies%2C%20which%20the%20EC%2C%20incredibly%2C%20explains%20away%20using%20an%20all-encompassing%20%E2%80%9Cprovisional%E2%80%9D%20tag.%20But%20the%20very%20fact%20that%20such%20discrepancies%20repeatedly%20occur%20between%20counts%20at%20the%20most%20granular%20(booth)%20level%20of%20the%20multiple%20stages%20of%20a%20single%20process%2C%20suggests%20the%20process%20needs%20significant%20improvement.%20And%20we%20cannot%20hope%20for%20such%20improvement%20without%20the%20additional%20investment%20of%20both%20resources%20and%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20spend%20more%20on%20elections%2C%20not%20less%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20this%20most%20sacred%20process%20of%20all%20democracy%2C%20functions%20with%20greater%20fairness%2C%20reliability%2C%20and%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDr.%20P.%20Thiaga%20Rajan%20is%20the%20MLA%20for%20Madurai%20Central%20Constituency%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%E2%80%99s%20Public%20Accounts%20Committee%2C%20and%20Head%20of%20the%20DMK%E2%80%99s%20IT%20Wing.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EViews%20are%20author%E2%80%99s%20own.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Farticle%2Fone-nation-one-poll-why-shred-fabric-constitution-help-parties-cut-costs-104201%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20News%20Minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693731191000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16163914%2F2048px-BMC_Election_2012_-_Ink_mark_after_voting_6886404209.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fone-nation-one-election-a-poor-argument-for-cost-savings-and-the-need-for-increased-poll-spending%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Estimates%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20holding%20state%20elections%20vary%20from%20around%20Rs%204%2C150%20crore%20every%20five%20years%20for%20all%20states%20combined%20to%20about%20Rs%205%2C500%20crore%20at%20an%20aggregate%20level.%20While%20this%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20it%20pales%20into%20insignificance%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20total%20state%20budgets%20over%20five%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fone-nation-one-election-a-poor-argument-for-cost-savings-and-the-need-for-increased-poll-spending%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Of%20Revolutions%2C%20Freedom%20%26amp%3B%20Love%20Stories%3A%2010%20Letters%20That%20Shaped%20India%E2%80%99s%20History%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20India%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%20letters%20have%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20%E2%80%94%20in%20driving%20revolutions%2C%20calling%20for%20freedom%20of%20women%2C%20strengthening%20political%20relations%20and%20diplomatic%20ties%2C%20and%20keeping%20thousands%20of%20love%20stories%20alive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetters%20led%20to%20elephants%20being%20sent%20to%20Tokyo%2C%20setting%20up%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20Indian%20Psychoanalytical%20Society%20and%20led%20to%20Anandibai%20Joshi%20becoming%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20female%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%2010%20such%20letters%20that%20have%20left%20an%20indelible%20mark%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20history%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20letter%20that%20helped%20Indians%20in%20Fiji%20end%20unpaid%20labour%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2Fmanilal-doctor-1-1681542921.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manilal%20Doctor%20provided%20legal%20assistance%20to%20Indians%20in%20Fiji.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%