u-Elephant-Letter-Feature-Image-1671264228-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FNehru-Elephant-Letter-Feature-Image-1671264228-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FNehru-Elephant-Letter-Feature-Image-1671264228-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-306419%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENehru%20sent%20an%20elephant%20named%20Indira%20to%20Japan.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20must%20look%20upon%20this%20elephant%20as%20a%20messenger%20of%20affection%20and%20goodwill%20from%20the%20children%20of%20India.%20The%20elephant%20is%20a%20noble%20animal.%20It%20is%20wise%20and%20patient%2C%20strong%20and%20yet%2C%20gentle.%20I%20hope%20all%20of%20us%20will%20also%20develop%20these%20qualities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%227%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20letter%20that%20led%20to%20toilets%20in%20Indian%20railways%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201012px)%20100vw%2C%201012px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2Findian-toilet-Letter-1661433608.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221012%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20letter%20that%20led%20to%20toilets%20in%20Indian%20railways.%20Image%3A%20Change%20Started%5Cn%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2Findian-toilet-Letter-1661433608.jpg%201012w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2Findian-toilet-Letter-1661433608-300x226.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2Findian-toilet-Letter-1661433608-500x377.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2Findian-toilet-Letter-1661433608-768x579.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2