e%20for%20the%20people%20involved%20in%20this%20work.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frecykal-3-1693229229.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frecykal-3-1693229229-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frecykal-3-1693229229-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frecykal-3-1693229229-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frecykal-3-1693229229-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-328366%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThrough%20its%20app%2C%20Recykal%20has%20set%20out%20to%20provide%20a%20better%20life%20for%20the%20people%20involved%20in%20this%20work.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecykal%E2%80%99s%20AI-driven%20marketplace%2C%20explains%20Abhishek%2C%20provides%20a%20forecast%20of%20market%20rates%20with%20up%20to%2095%20percent%20accuracy%20to%20purchase%20the%20scrap.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20then%20matches%20the%20quality%20of%20material%20collected%20with%20the%20expectations%20of%20recyclers%20and%20finally%20facilitates%20the%20sale%20of%20this%20material%20with%20support%20for%20logistics%20and%20hassle-free%20payments.%20This%20price%20prediction%2C%20lower%20logistics%20costs%2C%20higher%20returns%2C%20and%20timely%20payments%2C%20all%20help%20their%20businesses%20thrive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20boosting%20the%20income%20of%20scrap%20dealers%20up%20to%2036%20percent%2C%20the%20company%20was%20able%20to%20channelise%20seven%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20waste%20last%20year%20and%20generate%20an%20annual%20revenue%20of%20Rs%20745%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%202027%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20bring%2010%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20waste%20into%20circulation%20and%20help%20sav