original%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20brass%20vessels%20that%20were%20used%20for%20cooking%20back%20in%20the%20day.%20Everything%20is%20designed%20around%20taking%20the%20guests%20back%20a%20100%20years%2C%20yet%20feeling%20luxurious%20in%20the%20same%20moment.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20who%20thinks%20this%20is%20the%20main%20draw%20at%20Woodway%2C%20it%20gets%20better.%20The%20food%20is%20a%20completely%20different%20magic%20in%20itself.%20Susmitha%20says%20that%20the%20secret%20lies%20in%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286607%2Ffriends-quit-job-to-build-ecofriendly-home-stay-for-weekend-getaway-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekitchen%20garden%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20from%20where%20they%20source%20around%2070%20percent%20of%20their%20total%20produce.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMother%20Nature%20provides%20us%20with%20colocasia%2C%20mushrooms%2C%20aubergines%2C%20jackfruits%2C%20horse%20gram%2C%20turmeric%20leaves%2C%20pomelo%2C%20red%20rice%2C%20pepper%20and%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20traditional%20meal%20at%20Woodway%20includes%20%3Cem%3Eakki%20roti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20flatbread%20made%20with%20rice%20flour%2C%20spices%20and%20herbs)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekai%20kadubu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(coconut%20rice%20dumplings)%2C%20%3Cem%3Eurali%20kattu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20Karnataka%20speciality%20made%20with%20horse%20gram%20in%20spicy%20coconut%20gravy)%20and%20%3Cem%3Esevige%20kaihaalu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20sweet%20coconut%20milk%20side%20dish).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20that%20as%20he%20sees%20so%20many%20people%20now%20starting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290101%2Fbest-homestay-in-himachal-pradesh-sainj-valley-eco-friendly-kath-kuni-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomestays%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Shreedev%20says%20it%20